valueOf

public static TextLocalizable valueOf(java.lang.String template)
Create a TextLocalizable from a given template. A qualified global string is of the form resouceDomainName:label. If the given string template does not contain a resouceDoamineName it will be considered the text is already translated and will be used as is.

Parameters:
template - the template string.
Returns:
the corresponding TextLocalizable.

Parameters:

params - the parameters to inclue in the translated label.
